        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Nine years after university, An Ran is a career-driven entrepreneur with dreams of success. When a stunt to attract investors backfires, she ends up drunk and spends a \"romantic\" evening with her landlord, unknowingly her college junior, Yan Yue, who has secretly harbored feelings for her. Yan Yue, a successful voice actor, is also involved in a new project with An Ran, forcing them to spend more time together. Yan Yue hopes\n\nto rekindle their connection, but will An Ran feel the same?",
